title: Gunman kills one, wounds eight in Israeli city of Beersheba
text:
Gunman kills one, wounds eight in Israeli city of Beersheba 
Published By: Reuters - Today 
JERUSALEM (Reuters) - A gunman went on a stabbing and shooting rampage at the central bus station in the southern Israeli city of Beersheba ...
